channel.title: mycatalog updates
channel.description: 'My Catalog' uses the IBM Cloud catalog API to retrieve data from the catalog. It attempts to be as accurate as possible. This feed shows additions, updates, removals from the catalog. Use with care. It is a work-in-progress :)

item.title: [updated] Bespoken Automated Testing For IVR and Chat (automated-testing-and-monitoring-for-voice-and-chat) has a new plan named automated-testing-and-monitoring-for-voice-and-chat-load-testing
item.description: Use this plan to help you identify the maximum operating capacity of your conversational IVR as well as any bottlenecks and determine which element is causing degradation.
